snippet.title: Age of the Ring | Adventure Rhûn - showmatch
snippet.description:
8.0 available now: https://www.moddb.com/mods/the-horse-lords-a-total-modification-for-bfme/downloads

A match with no commentary showcasing the visuals and audio of the Rhûn adventure map. 

Age of the Ring is a mod for BFME2 Rise of the Witch-king. You need the original game to play it. 

Visit our Moddb page:
https://www.moddb.com/mods/the-horse-lords-a-total-modification-for-bfme
